reviewText: Very disappointed with this video. The quality is low. Shaky video, with cloudy and gloomy views. There are much better videos of Paris on the market than this.

So happy I came across this blu ray.  Been looking for a some kind of video for my indoor walking.  Pretty decent.  Glad I got the blu ray as I have a 60' tv.  A few minutes at the beginning were a little anoying as this was shot in a rainy day and you see rain drops on the camera.
